    title="The Accounts Hub"
    subtitle="From daily, weekly or monthly support with accounts payable for your business, The Knack Hub can assist with the following:"
    columns={3}
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Financial records',
        description:
          "Create, manage, and produce financial records that track cash flow and payments to vendors and suppliers. These records are important for a business's financial health.",
        icon: 'tabler:award',
      },
      {
        title: 'Record transactions',
        description:
          'Accurately and promptly record transactions. This requires good time management and attention to detail. ',
        icon: 'tabler:home-star',
      },
      {
        title: 'Communication',
        description: `Communicate with other departments and team members. Effective communication is important for establishing record-keeping procedures and collaborating on tasks.`,
        icon: 'tabler:clock',
      },
      {
        title: 'Supplier relationships',
        description:
          'Develop relationships with suppliers. Businesses often buy large amounts of goods from trusted suppliers, so effective account payable records are important for maintaining productive business relationships and resolving debts.',
        icon: 'tabler:shopping-cart',
      },
      {
        title: 'Outstanding payments',
        description: 'Follow up on outstanding payments.',
        icon: 'tabler:building-store',
      },
      {
        title: 'Account reconciliation',
        description: 'Reconcile monthly payable reports',
        icon: 'tabler:arrow-big-up-lines',
      },
      {
        title: 'Queries',
        description: `Respond to queries from customers, suppliers, and staff.`,
        icon: 'tabler:sun',
      },
      {
        title: 'Account discrepancies',
        description: `Resolve account discrepancies by investigating documentation, issuing stop payments, and adjustments.`,
        icon: 'tabler:sun',
      },
      {
        title: 'Financial security',
        description: `Maintain financial security by following internal accounting controls.`,
        icon: 'tabler:sun',
      },
      {
        title: 'Expense statements',
        description: `Prepare monthly expense statements and financial reports.`,
        icon: 'tabler:sun',
      },
    ]}
